snippet.title: Best VGM 1402 - Ys II Chronicles - Tender People (Ramia Village)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1537 - http://youtu.be/0YN7-nirAbk

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PSP / PC
Ys II Chronicles (2009)
Tender People (Ramia Village)
Mieko Ishikawa & Yukihiro Jindo
